@begin(outer)
  Outer body, indented.

  @begin(middle)
    Middle body.

    @begin(inner)
      Deepest, three levels in.
    @end(inner)
  @end(middle)
@end(outer)

@begin(note)
  Indented body with a code fence whose internal indentation survives:

  ```python
  def f():
      return 1
  ```
@end(note)
